{"tid":634102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[支付寳HK][好朋友手牽手互助]","createTime":"2018-04-19T02:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T07:26:31.000Z","uid":137040,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8384b5f4d73acbcbaebfdab8bfb375989ade14","tid":634102,"uid":137040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"P2P友情大激賞 <br />\n支付寶HK用戶向身邊任何好友轉賬任何金額，即可隨機獲贈$1.8至$88獎賞。即係話，過錢HK$0.1俾朋友都可以賺到HK$1.8－HK$88電子現金券！若你轉賬給未用過AlipayHK的親友，而你是第一個轉賬給他，即有機會抽到HK$18－HK$88電子現金券；若你的朋友已用過Alipay付款/轉帳，即有機會抽到HK$1.8－HK$8.8電子現金券。<br />\n<br />\n留意返：<br />\n<br />\n每人每天限50次，推廣期內限抽100次<br />\n電子現金券有效期只有15天，所以唔好一次過轉賬晒<br />\n同一付款用戶向同一收款用戶轉賬多次，推廣期間僅限獲享獎賞1次<br />\n推廣期：即日起至2018年5月31日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/101841_a28daf59963ff509c2d4e41f5e7eaec1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F101841_a28daf59963ff509c2d4e41f5e7eaec1.jpg&h=2aa0e4cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d23a4b8606058b8f63730729149fd7eb85e2655","tid":634102,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"98a80d922775244eba67888a7a8c9629b36a7ffc","tid":634102,"uid":172020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"真？"},{"pid":"33d627d1c95cb2bbaf6be7996b8b84349d309ca2","tid":634102,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"過比你最多都係得1.8，咁我不如洗contact list"}]}